text: Walnut Creek is a stream in Linn County, Kansas and Bates County, Missouri in the United States. It is a tributary of the Marais des Cygnes River.Missouri Atlas & Gasetteer, DeLorme, 1st ed, 1998, p. 42 Walnut Creek was named for the black walnut timber along its course. ==See also== *List of rivers of Missouri ==References== Category:Rivers of Linn County, Kansas Category:Rivers of Bates County, Missouri Category:Rivers of Kansas Category:Rivers of Missouri
title: Walnut Creek (Marais des Cygnes River tributary)
